 is the OFFICIAL annual flagship event under the Takaful banner – a prestigious and purpose-driven gathering now entering its third year. Over the years, TLAS has evolved into the industry’s iconic platform for showcasing leadership excellence, fostering innovation, and celebrating achievements. It stands as the premium stage for networking, learning, and recognition, uniting the Takaful community in shaping the future of the industry.</p><p>This summit is not just a training or networking day – it is a mark of belonging to the elite core of the Takaful community. Attendees will gain exclusive access to top-tier speakers, MDRT achievers, and industry decision-makers, with crowd-pulling attractions designed to inspire, connect, and elevate careers.</p><p></p><p>The Takaful Leader &amp; Agent Summit (TLAS) 2025 is a strategic initiative under the Hijrah 27 transformation plan, designed to drive the Takaful industry towards greater innovation, leadership excellence, and sustainable impact. This summit serves as a key enabler of Hijrah 27’s objectives by providing a platform for industry professionals to develop their leadership skills, embrace digitalisation, and reinforce ethical and value-driven business practices.</p><p></p><p>TLAS 2025 will introduce new thematic directions, focusing on strengthening industry-wide collaboration, embracing technological advancements, and positioning Takaful as a sustainable and resilient financial solution. This proposal outlines the summit’s theme, objectives, programme structure, budget, and expected outcomes to ensure alignment with the long-term vision of Hijrah 27.</p>\";s:8:\"start_at\";s:19:\"2025-11-01 12:14:00\";s:6:\"end_at\";s:19:\"2025-11-01 12:14:00\";s:5:\"venue\";s:30:\"Kuala Lumpur Convention Centre\";s:4:\"city\";s:12:\"Kuala Lumpur\";s:5:\"state\";s:19:\"Wilayah Persekutuan\";s:7:\"country\";s:8:\"Malaysia\";s:16:\"registration_url\";N;s:11:\"gdrive_link\";N;s:8:\"media_id\";i:3;s:18:\"venue_map_media_id\";N;s:12:\"is_published\";i:1;s:12:\"rsvp_enabled\";i:1;s:13:\"rsvp_deadline\";s:19:\"2025-10-29 12:14:00\";s:13:\"max_attendees\";i:500;s:16:\"require_approval\";i:0;s:9:\"meta_json\";N;s:10:\"created_at\";s:19:\"2026-02-24 12:14:37\";s:10:\"updated_at\";s:19:\"2026-02-26 15:45:20\";}s:11:\"\0*\0original\";a:23:{s:2:\"id\";i:1;s:5:\"title\";s:30:\"Takaful Leadership Summit 2025\";s:4:\"slug\";s:30:\"takaful-leadership-summit-2025\";s:7:\"excerpt\";s:91:\"The premier annual gathering of takaful industry leaders to discuss trends and innovations.\";s:12:\"content_html\";s:1828:\"<img class=\"rounded-lg max-w-full my-4\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/storage/media/2026/02/abbb6a90-0dd9-43e9-861b-62665ae2561a.jpeg\"><p>The Takaful Leader &amp; Agent Summit (TLAS) 2025 is the OFFICIAL annual flagship event under the Takaful banner – a prestigious and purpose-driven gathering now entering its third year. Over the years, TLAS has evolved into the industry’s iconic platform for showcasing leadership excellence, fostering innovation, and celebrating achievements. It stands as the premium stage for networking, learning, and recognition, uniting the Takaful community in shaping the future of the industry.</p><p>This summit is not just a training or networking day – it is a mark of belonging to the elite core of the Takaful community. Attendees will gain exclusive access to top-tier speakers, MDRT achievers, and industry decision-makers, with crowd-pulling attractions designed to inspire, connect, and elevate careers.</p><p></p><p>The Takaful Leader &amp; Agent Summit (TLAS) 2025 is a strategic initiative under the Hijrah 27 transformation plan, designed to drive the Takaful industry towards greater innovation, leadership excellence, and sustainable impact. This summit serves as a key enabler of Hijrah 27’s objectives by providing a platform for industry professionals to develop their leadership skills, embrace digitalisation, and reinforce ethical and value-driven business practices.</p><p></p><p>TLAS 2025 will introduce new thematic directions, focusing on strengthening industry-wide collaboration, embracing technological advancements, and positioning Takaful as a sustainable and resilient financial solution. This proposal outlines the summit’s theme, objectives, programme structure, budget, and expected outcomes to ensure alignment with the long-term vision of Hijrah 27.</p>\";s:8:\"start_at\";s:19:\"2025-11-01 12:14:00\";s:6:\"end_at\";s:19:\"2025-11-01 12:14:00\";s:5:\"venue\";s:30:\"Kuala Lumpur Convention Centre\";s:4:\"city\";s:12:\"Kuala Lumpur\";s:5:\"state\";s:19:\"Wilayah Persekutuan\";s:7:\"country\";s:8:\"Malaysia\";s:16:\"registration_url\";N;s:11:\"gdrive_link\";N;s:8:\"media_id\";i:3;s:18:\"venue_map_media_id\";N;s:12:\"is_published\";i:1;s:12:\"rsvp_enabled\";i:1;s:13:\"rsvp_deadline\";s:19:\"2025-10-29 12:14:00\";s:13:\"max_attendees\";i:500;s:16:\"require_approval\";i:0;s:9:\"meta_json\";N;s:10:\"created_at\";s:19:\"2026-02-24 12:14:37\";s:10:\"updated_at\";s:19:\"2026-02-26 15:45:20\";}s:10:\"\0*\0changes\";a:0:{}s:11:\"\0*\0previous\";a:0:{}s:8:\"\0*\0casts\";a:8:{s:8:\"start_at\";s:8:\"datetime\";s:6:\"end_at\";s:8:\"datetime\";s:12:\"is_published\";s:7:\"boolean\";s:12:\"rsvp_enabled\";s:7:\"boolean\";s:13:\"rsvp_deadline\";s:8:\"datetime\";s:13:\"max_attendees\";s:7:\"integer\";s:16:\"require_approval\";s:7:\"boolean\";s:9:\"meta_json\";s:5:\"array\";}s:17:\"\0*\0classCastCache\";a:0:{}s:21:\"\0*\0attributeCastCache\";a:0:{}s:13:\"\0*\0dateFormat\";N;s:10:\"\0*\0appends\";a:1:{i:0;s:6:\"status\";}s:19:\"\0*\0dispatchesEvents\";a:0:{}s:14:\"\0*\0observables\";a:0:{}s:12:\"\0*\0relations\";a:1:{s:5:\"media\";O:16:\"App\\Models\\Media\":33:{s:13:\"\0*\0connection\";s:5:\"mysql\";s:8:\"\0*\0table\";s:5:\"media\";s:13:\"\0*\0primaryKey\";s:2:\"id\";s:10:\"\0*\0keyType\";s:3:\"int\";s:12:\"incrementing\";b:1;s:7:\"\0*\0with\";a:0:{}s:12:\"\0*\0withCount\";a:0:{}s:19:\"preventsLazyLoading\";b:0;s:10:\"\0*\0perPage\";i:15;s:6:\"exis