INSERT INTO `events` VALUES (1,'Takaful Leadership Summit 2025','takaful-leadership-summit-2025','The premier annual gathering of takaful industry leaders to discuss trends and innovations.','<img class=\"rounded-lg max-w-full my-4\" src=\"http://localhost:8000/storage/media/2026/02/abbb6a90-0dd9-43e9-861b-62665ae2561a.jpeg\"><p>The Takaful Leader &amp; Agent Summit (TLAS) 2025 is the OFFICIAL annual flagship event under the Takaful banner – a prestigious and purpose-driven gathering now entering its third year. Over the years, TLAS has evolved into the industry’s iconic platform for showcasing leadership excellence, fostering innovation, and celebrating achievements. It stands as the premium stage for networking, learning, and recognition, uniting the Takaful community in shaping the future of the industry.</p><p>This summit is not just a training or networking day – it is a mark of belonging to the elite core of the Takaful community. Attendees will gain exclusive access to top-tier speakers, MDRT achievers, and industry decision-makers, with crowd-pulling attractions designed to inspire, connect, and elevate careers.</p><p></p><p>The Takaful Leader &amp; Agent Summit (TLAS) 2025 is a strategic initiative under the Hijrah 27 transformation plan, designed to drive the Takaful industry towards greater innovation, leadership excellence, and sustainable impact. This summit serves as a key enabler of Hijrah 27’s objectives by providing a platform for industry professionals to develop their leadership skills, embrace digitalisation, and reinforce ethical and value-driven business practices.</p><p></p><p>TLAS 2025 will introduce new thematic directions, focusing on strengthening industry-wide collaboration, embracing technological advancements, and positioning Takaful as a sustainable and resilient financial solution. This proposal outlines the summit’s theme, objectives, programme structure, budget, and expected outcomes to ensure alignment with the long-term vision of Hijrah 27.</p>','2025-11-01 12:14:00','2025-11-01 12:14:00','Kuala Lumpur Convention Centre','Kuala Lumpur','Wilayah Persekutuan','Malaysia',NULL,NULL,3,NULL,1,1,'2025-10-29 12:14:00',500,0,NULL,'2026-02-24 04:14:37','2026-02-26 07:45:20'),(3,'Takaful4All Larian Hero Hijau','takaful4all-larian-hero-hijau',NULL,'','2024-12-15 12:14:00','2024-12-15 12:14:00','Taman Tugu','Kuala Lumpur',NULL,'Malaysia',NULL,NULL,29,NULL,1,0,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'2026-02-24 04:14:37','2026-02-24 08:12:43'),(4,'Takaful4All Sustainability Day','takaful4all-sustainability-day','The Malaysian Takaful Association (MTA) is looking forward to meet you at the Takafu4Alll Sustainability Day 2024, themed “Protect, Care, Sustain”. This event is part of the Hijrah 27 Working Group 4 initiative which is championing the Takaful Industry’s ESG and Sustainability initiatives.','<p>The Malaysian Takaful Association (MTA) is looking forward to meet you at the <strong>Takafu4Alll Sustainability Day 2024</strong>, themed<strong>&nbsp;“Protect, Care, Sustain”</strong>. This event is part of the <strong>Hijrah 27 Working Group 4</strong>&nbsp;initiative which is championing the Takaful Industry’s ESG and Sustainability initiatives.&nbsp;</p><p>Our vision is simple but yet powerful: to inspire everyone, especially the younger generation, to adopt sustainable practices and environmental conservation in their daily lives. This fun-filled day promises something for everyone which will feature interactive and hands-on activities designed to connect everyone with nature whilst promoting good health, fostering a deeper understanding and commitment to sustainability.&nbsp;</p><p>Highlights of the events:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Larian Hero Hijau</strong>: A refreshing 5 kilo meter morning fun-run at perimeter of Taman Tugu to kickstart the day.</p></li><li><p><strong>Zero Waste Lifestyle Workshop</strong>: Learn practical steps toward sustainable living with Zero Waste Malaysia.</p></li><li><p><strong>Launch of Takaful4All Disaster Response Team</strong>: Witness the unveiling of this impactful initiative by Takaful Industry in expanding its Disaster Response Team – don’t miss the chance to register for the Takaful Disaster Taskforce, which is co-organized with Jabatan Bomba dan Penyelamat Malaysia.</p></li><li><p><strong>Sustainability Carnival</strong>: Engage in eco-friendly workshops, art, photography, and financial &amp; sustainability literacy activities.</p></li><li><p><strong>Folks Sport Activities:</strong>&nbsp;Relive your childhood memories through “Timbang Bulu Ayam” and “Musang Berjanggut” games to bring back the good old days</p></li><li><p><strong>Coloring Contest:</strong>&nbsp;Educating the children on preserving nature for sustainability&nbsp;</p></li><li><p><strong>Takaful Sustainability Booth:</strong>&nbsp;Showcase of Sustainability activities or Takaful Products by 15 Takaful Operators</p></li></ul><p>We would love for this event to be a day of fun, learning, and connection—not just for you but also for your teams, families, and friends. We kindly ask for your support in spreading the word by sharing this invitation across your organisation to ensure everyone has the opportunity to join us.</p>','2024-12-15 12:14:00','2024-12-15 17:14:00','Taman Tugu Nursery','Kuala Lumpur','Wilayah Persekutuan','Malaysia',NULL,NULL,30,NULL,1,0,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'2026-02-24 04:14:37','2026-02-24 08:14:21'),(5,'Takaful4All Inter-TO Bowling Tournament','takaful4all-inter-to-bowling-tournament','This tournament is one of MTA’s initiatives to create a “Healthy Lifestyle” culture among its member companies through sportsmanship. In addition, through the organization of this sports tournament, it is also hoped to create sportsmanship among the takaful industry in addition to unearthing hidden talents.','<p>The objectives of the Bowling Tournament are:</p><ul><li><p>Strengthening the Healthy Lifestayle culture by organising events that encourage social interaction, enjoyment, and a sense of belonging among MTA member employees.</p></li><li><p>Creating opportunities for MTA member employees from different departments or levels of the organisation to connect and network in a casual and informal setting, potentially fostering cross-departmental collaboration and communication.</p></li><li><p>Encouraging friendly competition among MTA member companies, which can promote a sense of achievement and satisfaction as well as help develop a competitive spirit in a positive context</p></li></ul><p>This tournament is one of MTA’s initiatives to create a “Healthy Lifestyle” culture among its member companies through sportsmanship. In addition, through the organization of this sports tournament, it is also hoped to create sportsmanship among the takaful industry in addition to unearthing hidden talents.</p>','2024-06-01 14:02:00','2024-06-01 14:30:00','Sunway Pyramid',NULL,NULL,'Malaysia',NULL,NULL,31,NULL,1,0,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'2026-02-24 08:16:10','2026-02-24 08:16:10'),(6,'Test Event','test-event','test-eventtest-eventtest-eventtest-event','<p>test-eventtest-eventtest-eventtest-event</p>','2026-04-24 08:00:00','2026-04-30 17:00:00','Sunway Pyramid',NULL,NULL,'Malaysia',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,1,'2026-03-26 00:00:00',190,0,NULL,'2026-02-26 08:05:37','2026-02-26 08:05:37'),(7,'Takaful Leadership Summit 2026','takaful-leadership-summit-2026','The premier annual gathering of takaful industry leaders to discuss trends and innovations.','<p>Join us for the <strong>Takaful Leadership Summit 2026</strong>, an exclusive conference bringing together CEOs, regulators, and innovators from across the global takaful industry.</p><p>This year\'s theme: <em>\"Resilience Through Innovation\"</em>.</p><h2>Key Topics</h2><ul><li>Digital transformation in takaful</li><li>Regulatory updates from BNM</li><li>Sustainable takaful products</li></ul>','2026-03-28 17:21:21','2026-03-29 17:21:21','Kuala Lumpur Convention Centre','Kuala Lumpur','Wilayah Persekutuan','Malaysia','https://events.takaful4all.org/register/summit-2026',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,0,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'2026-02-26 09:21:21','2026-02-26 09:21:21'),(8,'Takaful Innovation Conference 2026','takaful-innovation-conference-2026','Exploring the future of InsurTech and takaful digital products.','<p>A full-day conference focused on <strong>digital innovation</strong> across the takaful value chain.</p>','2026-04-27 17:21:00','2026-04-28 01:21:00','Pullman Kuala Lumpur City Centre','Kuala Lumpur','Wilayah Persekutuan','Malaysia','https://events.takaful4all.org/register/innovation-2026',NULL,34,38,1,1,'2026-04-22 17:21:00',300,1,NULL,'2026-02-26 09:21:21','2026-04-15 07:54:06'),(9,'Takaful Awareness Week 2025','takaful-awareness-week-2025','A week-long initiative to educate the public about takaful benefits.','<p>Takaful Awareness Week 2025 brought together <strong>over 2,000 participants</strong> across Malaysia for workshops, seminars, and public outreach events.</p>','2025-11-18 17:21:21','2025-11-25 17:21:21','Various Locations Nationwide','Multiple Cities','Nationwide','Malaysia',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,0,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'2026-02-26 09:21:21','2026-02-26 09:21:21'),(10,'MTA Annual Dinner & Awards 2025','mta-annual-dinner-awards-2025','Celebrating excellence and achievements in the Malaysian takaful industry.','<p>The <strong>MTA Annual Dinner & Awards 2025</strong> was a night to remember — celebrating the best of the takaful industry.</p>','2025-08-10 17:21:21','2025-08-10 22:21:21','Mandarin Oriental Kuala Lumpur','Kuala Lumpur','Wilayah Persekutuan','Malaysia',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,0,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'2026-02-26 09:21:21','2026-02-26 09:21:21');
